Package: thesisvink
Type: Package
Title: Package with functions used for my Master Thesis and Research Report
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pepijn", "Vink", email = "p.a.vink@uu.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6960-9904"))
    )
Description: This package can be used to simulate data under a specific data generating mechanism with 2 time-invariant confounders.
   It also contains functions to analyze these useing the RI-CLPM and DPM as well as to check these for convergence.
